title: Critérium du Dauphiné stage 7: Jonas Vingegaard dominates in pre-Tour de France demonstration
content:
Vingegaard kicks out of the GC group 5km from the line for solo victory in race's 'queen stage,' extends overall lead.

Read the full article at Critérium du Dauphiné stage 7: Jonas Vingegaard dominates in pre-Tour de France demonstration on Velo.
